data.description: MAKE THE MOVE -- GATED ACCESS COMMUNITY with convenient access to all that Houston has to offer. Just minutes from the Medical Center, Houston Museum District, Hermann Park, and access to all the greatest shopping and dining options around. This STUNNING 3 bed, 2.5 with NO REAR NEIGHBORS features GRANITE ISLAND kitchen, modern 42" cabinetry, tile backsplash, breakfast bar, & stainless appliances. Kitchen opens to family room that features accent wall and an abundance of natural lighting. Rich vinyl wood flooring on first floor, neutral paint colors, recessed lighting, and high ceilings. All rooms up with two spacious secondary bedrooms and PRIMARY RETREAT with french door access, trey ceiling, dual vanities, soaking tub, & oversized shower. Cozy back patio -- perfect for entertaining. Community offers lake, jogging trail, and dog park. Call for your private showing!!!
